<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Pray for the peace of Jerusalem!</para>

<para style="q1">"May those who love you have peace.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />May there be peace within the walls that defend you,</para>

<para style="q1">and may they have peace within your fortresses."</para>
